These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, azure, blue
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, turtle, mouse
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, fantasy, superhero
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, october
The people use 3 different means of transport: trike, bike, scooter
House: craftsman, modern, farmhouse
3 different games are played: scrabble, poker, monopoly
 1. the person playing scrabble is the modern house##1
 2. the person playing monopoly is the person who's birthday is in october##1
 3. the person who likes blue is between the farmhouse house and the person who likes azure##2
 4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the craftsman house##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is the owner of the mouse##1
 6. the person watching superhero movies is the craftsman house##1
 7. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
 9. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Color      | azure    | blue   | purple           |
| Pet          | turtle       | mouse    | guinea-pig         |
| Movie-Genre         | fantasy    | superhero  | crime        |
| Birthday           | april | january   | october      |
| Transport   | bike        | scooter    | trike       |
| House   | modern     | craftsman  | farmhouse       |
| Game         | scrabble     | poker | monopoly |

