The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, motorbike, subway
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, coach, project-manager
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, amber, aquamarine
House: cottage, victorian, palace
 1. the person who likes aquamarine is the coach##1
 2. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who growsbegonia##1
 3. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 4. the cottage house is between the prince-smoker and the tiparillo-smoker##2
 5. the project-manager is on the far left##1
 6. the prince-smoker is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the palace house##1
 8. the person playing scrabble is the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
10. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Cigar      | tiparillo   | bolivar    | prince         |
| Game          | scrabble    | poker | snooker          |
| Flower   | dahlia  | begonia  | orchid     |
