.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, boat, bike
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, firefighter, police-officer
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, mah-jongg
City: paris, new-york, hannover
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, daisy, sunflower
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, water, mirinda
House: townhouse, art-deco, gothic-revival
 1. the person driving the boat is the person drinking water##1
 2. the person who growssunflower is the firefighter##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the person playing scrabble is the person drinking water##1
 5. the art-deco house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 7. the police-officer is between the person who growsdaisy and the person traveling to hannover##2
 8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the right of the townhouse house##1
10. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
11. the person who growsdaisy is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Transport          | bike      | boat      | airplane      |
| Job         | pilot   | police-officer | firefighter |
| Game   | backgammon | scrabble    | mah-jongg          |
| City   | new-york       | paris      | hannover          |
| Flower   | daisy    | rose  | sunflower      |
| Beverage           | juice   | water  | mirinda        |
| House         | townhouse  | art-deco   | gothic-revival     |

