 6. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 7. the person who likes grey is the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person who growsiris is the person traveling to paris##1
 9. the person eating raspberry is between the person who growsiris and the person who growsazalea##2
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
