The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, traveling, fishing
 1. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is the person who likes pink##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1
 5. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes black and the person who growssunflower##2
 6. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes azure and the person watching time-travel movies##2
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 8. the person who growslily is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
 9. the mexican is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the chinese is the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
