The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, salsa, ambient
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, chef, software-developer
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, zinnia, begonia
 1. the software-developer is in the middle##1
 2. the person eating peach is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the fan ambient is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is between the person eating potato and the person who likes green##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the librarian##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who growsdaffodil##1
10. the fan ambient is on the left of the fan salsa##1
11. the person who growsdaffodil is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Food      | potato | peach      | blueberry      |
| City         | boston     | hamburg     | paris  |
| Birthday   | june | august  | november |
| Color   | blood-red  | chestnut     | green |
| Music-Genre           | soul        | ambient | salsa     |
| Job         | librarian    | software-developer | chef   |
| Flower     | zinnia        | begonia        | daffodil   |

