.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, cain, baccarat
3 different pets are kept: ferret, mouse, chinchilla
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, house, indie
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, brown, purple
House: palace, ranch-style, gothic-revival
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, daisy, rose
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, colombian, british
1. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
2. the british is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
4. the person who growssunflower is between the palace house and the person who likes brown##2
5. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who likes purple and the fan indie##2
6. the fan house is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
8. the polish is on the left of the baccarat-smoker##1
9. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester      | cain      | baccarat       |
| Pet          | mouse      | chinchilla    | ferret   |
| Music-Genre         | indie    | trance     | house     |
| Color           | brown    | apricot | purple   |
| House   | ranch-style    | gothic-revival    | palace       |
| Flower         | rose | sunflower      | daisy    |
| Nationality     | colombian       | polish | british |

