.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
3 different games are played: billiard, monopoly, domino
House: farmhouse, cottage, futuristic
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, adventure, thriller
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, january, september
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dunhill, fonseca
City: london, marseilles, hannover
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, dubstep, electronic
1. the person playing billiard is the futuristic house##1
2. the fan electronic is the person traveling to london##1
3. the person watching action movies is between the person playing domino and the fonseca-smoker##2
4. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the fan electronic##1
5. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the fan dubstep is on the left of the fan electronic##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is the farmhouse house##1
8. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
9. the person who's birthday is in january is between the farmhouse house and the fan reggae##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Game      | monopoly    | billiard       | domino      |
| House          | farmhouse   | futuristic   | cottage  |
| Movie-Genre           | adventure  | action | thriller    |
| Birthday   | july   | january     | september  |
| Cigar           | fonseca     | havana        | dunhill |
| City         | marseilles | london   | hannover  |
| Music-Genre     | dubstep    | electronic     | reggae      |

 